{"tid":2172194,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"你G唔G，我地好耐以前曾經光復過香港？","createTime":"2020-08-24T12:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T01:47:10.000Z","uid":211994,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f7a4e5e8930491710f62ba97ceb2d0d01ee8bcf9","tid":2172194,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:20:26.000Z","msg":"1945年8月30日，香港從日佔的「三年零八個月」黑暗歲月中重光，一步一步發展成我們曾經引以為傲的東方之珠，是為<span class=\"gold\">香港重光紀念日</span>。<br />\n<br />\n香港於1997年主權移交後，重光紀念日公眾假期遭取消，並和11月11日的和平紀念日合併，紀念儀式改於重陽節進行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chjsBAg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchjsBAg.jpg&h=dddfcef9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1945年重光勝利巡遊。（圖片來源：Wiki）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家可以睇下呢篇手足打嘅文章：</strong><a href=\"https://is.gd/0uuPYX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2F0uuPYX&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3Sbs4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=8e08a20c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/0uuPYX</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">我地成功過一次<br />\n就一定可以再成功多一次</span></span>"},{"pid":"c70a89f70c4271d676f3818e7097a3f95712cdf1","tid":2172194,"uid":329733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:22:31.000Z","msg":"8月30日重光紀念日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d9d45e2e174b75b94454214a11e330cdc4f1229","tid":2172194,"uid":171586,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:22:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"648140bda581837d517eb72c5b40e57fb69f27cb","tid":2172194,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:22:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca540b807edce0a1ca45c1773f08065d7aa388b0","tid":2172194,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:28:36.000Z","m